 galaxies and the\norigin of the first supermassive BH seeds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2013 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2013 19:52:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
